# 9ï¸âƒ£ HOW DevOps Works (Step by Step)

### Step 1: Culture Change

* Dev + Ops work together
* Shared ownership
* Same goal: **business success**

---

### Step 2: Training

* Dev learns Ops basics
* Ops learns Agile mindset
* Everyone understands end-to-end flow

---

### Step 3: Automation (Core of DevOps)

Everything is automated:

| Area       | Automation             |
| ---------- | ---------------------- |
| Code build | CI pipelines           |
| Testing    | Automated tests        |
| Infra      | Infrastructure as Code |
| Deployment | CD pipelines           |
| Monitoring | Alerts & dashboards    |

ðŸ“Œ No manual steps â†’ fewer errors

